---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/layout/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/layout/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="True Finance Tools — Free Financial Calculators for FIRE, Retirement & Smart Planning"
  description="Free financial calculators for FIRE planning, retirement, and investment decisions. Calculate your FIRE number, compare strategies, and build a roadmap to financial independence. No signup required."
  canonical="https://truefinancetools.com"
  ogImage="https://truefinancetools.com/og.png"
  ogImageAlt="True Finance Tools - Free Financial Calculators for FIRE and Retirement Planning"
  keywords="financial calculators, FIRE calculator, retirement calculator, financial independence calculator, early retirement planning, investment calculator, savings calculator, coast fire calculator, lean fire calculator, fat fire calculator"
>
  <Header />

  <main>
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden border-b border-hairline bg-canvas py-20 sm:py-28">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top,_var(--color-gradient-start)_0%,_transparent_50%)] opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 text-center sm:px-6">
        <p class="mb-4 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-mute">Free Calculator</p>

        <h1 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl" style="letter-spacing: -0.03em;">
          Plan Your Path to<br />Financial Independence
        </h1>

        <p class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-2xl text-base sm:text-lg text-body">
          Calculate your FIRE number, compare Lean, Regular, and Fat FIRE scenarios, and build a roadmap to early retirement.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
          <a
            href="/fire-calculator"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-ink px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-canvas transition-opacity hover:opacity-90"
          >
            Start Calculating
            <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
            </svg>
          </a>

          <a
            href="/learn/what-is-fire"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-hairline bg-canvas px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-ink transition-colors hover:bg-canvas-soft-2"
          >
            Learn About FIRE
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="border-b border-hairline bg-canvas py-16">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6">
        <h2 class="mb-6 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
          The Best FIRE Calculator for Early Retirement Planning
        </h2>
        
        <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none text-body">
          <p class="mb-4">
            Our free <strong>FIRE calculator</strong> helps you determine exactly how much money you need to achieve financial independence and retire early. Whether you're just starting your FIRE journey or are well on your way, this powerful retirement calculator provides instant, accurate projections based on your unique financial situation.
          </p>
          
          <p class="mb-4">
            The FIRE movement (Financial Independence, Retire Early) has helped thousands escape the traditional 9-to-5 grind. Our calculator supports multiple FIRE strategies including <strong>Lean FIRE</strong> for minimalist lifestyles, <strong>Regular FIRE</strong> for comfortable retirement, <strong>Fat FIRE</strong> for those wanting to maintain higher spending, and <strong>Coast FIRE</strong> for those who've saved enough to let compound interest finish the job.
          </p>

          <h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-ink">How Our FIRE Calculator Works</h3>
          
          <p class="mb-4">
            Simply enter your current age, target retirement age, annual income, savings rate, and expected investment returns. Our <strong>coast fire calculator</strong> instantly shows your projected portfolio growth, the year you'll reach financial independence, and exactly how much you need to save each month. The interactive charts visualize your path to FIRE, making it easy to see how different variables impact your timeline.
          </p>

          <p class="mb-4">
            Want to know what happens if you increase your savings rate by 5%? Or how market fluctuations might affect your retirement date? Our scenario comparison feature lets you test multiple strategies side by side. Compare <strong>barista fire calculator</strong> scenarios where you work part-time in retirement against full early retirement options.
          </p>

          <h3 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-ink">Why Choose Our Best Fire Calculator</h3>
          
          <p class="mb-4">
            Unlike other retirement calculators that require sign-ups or limit features behind paywalls, our <strong>fat fire calculator</strong> is completely free and private. No data is stored on our servers—everything runs in your browser. Get instant results with beautiful, interactive charts that update in real-time as you adjust your inputs.
          </p>

          <p class="mb-4">
            Export your personalized FIRE plan as a PDF, share it with your partner via a unique link, or save your progress for later. Our <strong>fire calculator retirement</strong> tool also includes a comprehensive FAQ section explaining key concepts like the 4% rule, safe withdrawal rates, and how to calculate your FIRE number.
          </p>

          <p class="mb-4">
            Whether you're calculating Coast FIRE to see when you can switch to a lower-stress job, exploring Barista FIRE for a hybrid work-retirement lifestyle, or planning full early retirement, our calculator provides the accurate projections you need to make informed financial decisions. Start planning your path to financial independence today—it's free, instant, and requires no signup.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="border-b border-hairline bg-canvas py-16">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6">
        <div class="mb-12 text-center">
          <p class="mb-2 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-mute">Features</p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
            Everything You Need to Plan Early Retirement
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6 shadow-sm">
            <div class="mb-4 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-canvas-soft-2 text-ink">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M15.75 15.75V18m-7.5-6.75h.008v.008H8.25v-.008zm0 2.25h.008v.008H8.25v-.008zm0 2.25h.008v.008H8.25v-.008zm0 2.25h.008v.008H8.25v-.008zm2.498-6.75h.007v.008h-.007v-.008zm0 2.25h.007v.008h-.007v-.008zm0 2.25h.007v.008h-.007v-.008zm0 2.25h.007v.008h-.007v-.008zm2.504-6.75h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 2.25h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 2.25h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 2.25h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm2.498-6.75h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 2.25h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zM8.25 6h7.5v2.25h-7.5V6zM12 2.25c-1.892 0-3.758.11-5.593.322C5.307 2.7 4.5 3.65 4.5 4.757V19.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25V4.757c0-1.108-.806-2.057-1.907-2.185A48.507 48.507 0 0012 2.25z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Multiple FIRE Types</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-body">Compare Lean, Regular, Fat, and Coast FIRE strategies to find what works for you.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6 shadow-sm">
            <div class="mb-4 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-canvas-soft-2 text-ink">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 013 19.875v-6.75zM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V8.625zM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V4.125z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Interactive Charts</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-body">Visualize your portfolio growth with beautiful, interactive charts and projections.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6 shadow-sm">
            <div class="mb-4 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-canvas-soft-2 text-ink">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M7.5 21L3 16.5m0 0L7.5 12M3 16.5h13.5m0-13.5L21 7.5m0 0L16.5 12M21 7.5H7.5" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Scenario Comparison</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-body">Compare different savings rates, investment returns, and retirement ages side by side.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6 shadow-sm">
            <div class="mb-4 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-canvas-soft-2 text-ink">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818l.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Coast FIRE Analysis</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-body">See when you've saved enough to let compound interest finish the job for you.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6 shadow-sm">
            <div class="mb-4 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-canvas-soft-2 text-ink">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M3 16.5v2.25A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0021 18.75V16.5M16.5 12L12 16.5m0 0L7.5 12m4.5 4.5V3" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Export & Share</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-body">Download your results as PDF or share your FIRE plan with a unique link.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6 shadow-sm">
            <div class="mb-4 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-canvas-soft-2 text-ink">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path d="M12 18v-5.25m0 0a6.01 6.01 0 001.5-.189m-1.5.189a6.01 6.01 0 01-1.5-.189m3.75 7.478a12.06 12.06 0 01-4.5 0m3.75 2.383a14.406 14.406 0 01-3 0M14.25 18v-.192c0-.983.658-1.823 1.508-2.316a7.5 7.5 0 10-7.517 0c.85.493 1.509 1.333 1.509 2.316V18" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Real-Time Calculations</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-body">Results update instantly as you adjust your inputs. No waiting, no page reloads.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="border-b border-hairline bg-canvas-soft py-16">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6">
        <div class="mb-12 text-center">
          <p class="mb-2 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-mute">How It Works</p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
            Simple Steps to Financial Independence
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-ink font-mono text-lg font-semibold text-canvas">1</div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Enter Your Details</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-body">Input your age, income, savings rate, expenses, and expected investment returns.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-ink font-mono text-lg font-semibold text-canvas">2</div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-ink">See Your FIRE Number</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-body">Get instant calculations showing how much you need and how long it will take.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-ink font-mono text-lg font-semibold text-canvas">3</div>
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-ink">Plan Your Journey</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-body">Compare scenarios, adjust your strategy, and export your personalized FIRE plan.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="border-b border-hairline bg-canvas py-16">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6">
        <div class="mb-12 text-center">
          <p class="mb-2 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-mute">Learn</p>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
            Start Your FIRE Journey
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <a href="/learn/what-is-fire" class="group rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-md">
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-ink group-hover:text-link">What is FIRE?</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-body">Learn the basics of Financial Independence, Retire Early and how it works.</p>
          </a>

          <a href="/learn/fire-strategies" class="group rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-md">
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-ink group-hover:text-link">FIRE Strategies</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-body">Discover different approaches to achieve financial independence.</p>
          </a>

          <a href="/learn/fire-number" class="group rounded-lg border border-hairline bg-canvas p-6 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-md">
            <h3 class="mb-2 text-sm font-semibold text-ink group-hover:text-link">Your FIRE Number</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-body">Calculate exactly how much you need to retire early.</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-canvas py-16">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 text-center sm:px-6">
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
          Ready to Start Planning?
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-8 text-body">Calculate your FIRE number in seconds. It's free, private, and no signup required.</p>

        <a
          href="/fire-calculator"
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-ink px-8 py-3 text-base font-medium text-canvas transition-opacity hover:opacity-90"
        >
          Open Calculator
          <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
